Intermediate Mechanical Engineer – MEP Contractor, Building Ser...
02 May 2014 06:44 AM - UAE
. Intermediate Mechanical Engineer – MEP Contractor, Building Services – Dubai, UAE My Client is a Mid-Sized contractor based in Dubai specialising in MEP Building Services across a variety of sectors. After a number of successful bids the MEP Contractor is looking to expand their team and add 2 Intermediate level Mechanical Engineers. Role & Responsibility of the Intermediate Mechanical Engineer The Intermediate level Mechanical Engineers will be responsible for reviewing design drawings and material submittals along with ensuring the smooth delivery of Mechanical Building Services in the MEP Contractors varied project portfolio. Required Experience for the Intermediate Mechanical Engineers • Circa 7-10 years of experience• A degree of diploma qualification from a recognised institution• Experience in the supervision of Mechanical site activities• Strong English language skills• Previous experience in Dubai• Experience in a Contracting firm• Understanding of UAE, Dubai & International Building codes Salary & Benefits: Salary negotiable plus allowances for accommodation and transportation per month plus flights, medical and annual leave. THIS IS AN URGENT REQUIREMENT PLEASE INDICATE YOU AVALIBILITY ON YOUR APPLICATION If you would like more information
